By: Chang Po-tuan
---
Even if your intelligence is above that of Yen-tzû and Min-tzû (two of
the most clever pupils of Confucius), yet, merely with constrained
conjecture, you will not be able to succeed unless you have a true
teacher. For the work of chin tan (gold medicine) in case oral
instructions are lacking, where and how can you fertilize the fecund
womb?
